{% extends '_layouts/base.njk' %}

{% block page_title %}Queen{% endblock %}

{% block page_description %}A project about the best band in the world.{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="img/queen-band-early.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Queen early days.">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="img/queen-live-on-stage.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Queen performing live on stage.">
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="bandSummary">
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Queen_(band)">Queen are a British rock band</a> formed in London in 1970. Their classic line-up was Freddie Mercury (lead vocals, piano), Brian May (guitar, vocals), Roger Taylor (drums, vocals) and John Deacon (bass). Their earliest works were influenced by progressive rock, hard rock and heavy metal, but the band gradually ventured into more conventional and radio-friendly works by incorporating further styles, such as arena rock and pop rock.
      </p>
      
      {% for member in queen.members %}
        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row-featurette">
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="member-headline"><a href="{{member.slug}}.html"> {{member.name}}</a></h2>
            <p class="lead">{{member.tenure}}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="member-image col-md-5">
            <img src="img/members/{{ member.imagebw }}" class="img-fluid">
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endfor%}

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
